CRIANDO PROJETO DO ZERO
. yarn create react-app first

ESLint, Prettier & EditorConfig
. Clique com o bot√£o direito do mouse e generate .editor config
. yarn add eslint -D
. yarn eslint --init
. Remover arquivo package-lock.json
. rodar 'yarn' na raiz do projeto pra atualizar as dependencias
. yarn add prettier eslint-config-prettier eslint-plugin-prettier babel-eslint -D
. Criar arquivo .prettierrc

CONFIGURANDO ROTAS
. yarn add react-router-dom

ESTILOS GLOBAIS
. yarn add styled-components

CRIANDO HEADER
. yarn add react-icons
. yarn add polished


CONFIGURANDO API
. yarn global add json-server
. yarn add axios
. json-server server.json -p 3333

CONFIGURANDO REDUX
. yarn add redux react-redux

REACTOTRON E REDUX
. yarn add reactotron-react-js reactotron-redux

Obs: Proptypes: npm install --save prop-types

PRODUTO DUPLICADO
. yarn add immer

CONFIGURANDO REDUX SAGA
. yarn add redux-saga

REACTOTRON + SAGA
. yarn add reactotron-redux-saga

REACT TOSTIFY
. yarn add react-toastify

NAVEGANDO NO SAGA
. yarn add history
